--  Boost version needed 1.65

Step 1:
https://www.boost.org/users/history/version_1_65_0.html
-- Download: boost_1_65_0.tar.gz

Step 2:
Open terminal and run:
cd Downloads/
tar -xzf boost_1_65_0.tar.gz 

Step 3:
Once unpackaged:
cd boost_1_65_0/

Step 4:
./bootstrap.sh --prefix=path/to/installation/prefix   (I.e - home/usr/Downloads/etc...)

Step 5:
./b2

Step 6:
./b2 install
